HEADWORD: Misreport
<hw>Mis`re*port"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t. & i.</pos> <def>To report
erroneously; to give an incorrect account of.</def>
<rj><au>Locke.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Misreport</ent>⟦br⟧

==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Misreport
<hw>Mis`re*port"</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>An erroneous report; a false
or incorrect account given.</def> <rj><au>Denham. South.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Misrepresent</ent>⟦br⟧
